        "additional_prompt": "STAGE: Validity of Cognition rating.\n\nAsk: 'When you think of the memory, how true do those words — [REPEAT THE POSITIVE COGNITION] — feel to you now, on a scale from 1 to 7, where 1 feels completely false and 7 feels completely true?'\n\nIf they're stuck, clarify: 'Sometimes we know something with our head but it feels differently in our gut. What's the gut-level number?'\n\nAccept any number 1–7. If they give a range ('like a 3 or 4'), gently ask for a single number.\n\nAdvance once you have a single number 1–7.",
        "additional_knowledge_base": [],
        "additional_tool_ids": [],
        "type": "override_agent",
        "position": {
          "x": -277.0325509355406,
          "y": 131.75287872474513
        },
        "edge_order": [
          "voc_to_emotion"
        ],
        "label": "VOC Rating (1–7)",
        "auto_advance_after_first_response": false
      },
      "emotion_node": {
        "conversation_config": {
